1. Download vagrant and virtual box.

2. cd ubuntu/

3. vagrant init ubuntu/xenial64 - initialize ubuntu xenial distribution

4. vagrant up - use virtual box to set ubuntu xenial box.

5. vagrant ssh

6. wget https://github.com/kubernetes/kops/releases/download/1.9.1/kops-linux-amd64

7. chmod +x kops-linux-amd64

8. sudo mv kops-linux-amd64 /usr/local/bin

9, sudo apt-get install software-properties-common

10. sudo apt-add-repository universe

11. sudo apt-get update

12. sudo apt-get install python-pip

13. sudo pip install awscli

14. 
